AmaterasuOS -- available commands

  echo [text]        print text to the screen
  uname [-a|-s|-r|-m] print kernel information
  hostname           print the system hostname
  wc [-l|-w|-c] <path>  count lines, words, and bytes
  head [-n N] <path>   print first N lines of a file
  tail [-n N] <path>   print last N lines of a file
  clear              clear the screen
  ls [path]          list directory contents
  cat <path>         print file contents
  stat <path>        show file metadata
  cd <path>          change working directory
  pwd                print current working directory
  cpu                show CPU vendor and brand string
  uptime             show system uptime
  heap               show heap allocator statistics
  reboot             restart the machine
  shutdown           power off the machine
  help [command]     show this help, or help for a specific command

Type 'help <command>' for detailed usage.
Type 'help tab' for tab completion tips.
